<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Confirmation de reservation</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1E5BA8, #6BBF59); color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-radius: 20px 20px 0 0; }
        .content { background: #f9f9f9; padding: 30px; border-radius: 0 0 20px 20px; }
        .qr-code { text-align: center; margin: 20px 0; padding: 20px; background: white; border-radius: 15px; }
        .qr-code img { max-width: 200px; border-radius: 10px; }
        .seat-info { background: #EFF7E6; padding: 15px; border-radius: 10px; text-align: center; margin: 20px 0; }
        .seat-number { font-size: 28px; font-weight: bold; color: #1E5BA8; }
        .impact-box { background: #eef6ff; padding: 18px; border-radius: 14px; margin: 20px 0; border: 1px solid #d6e6f7; }
        .impact-pill { display: inline-block; padding: 6px 10px; border-radius: 999px; background: #1E5BA8; color: #fff; font-size: 12px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; font-size: 12px; color: #999; }
        .btn { display: inline-block; background: #6BBF59; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 25px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Reservation confirmee</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Bonjour {{ reservation.nom }},</h2>
            <p>Votre reservation pour <strong>{{ reservation.evenement.titre }}</strong> a bien ete enregistree.</p>

            <div class="seat-info">
                <p><strong>Votre siege attribue</strong></p>
                <div class="seat-number">Siege {{ reservation.seatNumber }}</div>
                <p style="margin-top: 10px; font-size: 14px;">Presentez ce QR code a l entree.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="qr-code">
                <img src="{{ reservation.qrCode }}" alt="QR Code d entree">
            </div>

            <div style="margin: 20px 0;">
                <p><strong>Date :</strong> {{ reservation.evenement.date|date('d/m/Y H:i') }}</p>
                <p><strong>Lieu :</strong> {{ reservation.evenement.localisation }}</p>
                <p><strong>Billet :</strong> {{ reservation.ticketAmount|number_format(2, ',', ' ') }} TND</p>
                <p><strong>Montant total :</strong> {{ reservation.montantTotal|number_format(2, ',', ' ') }} TND</p>
            </div>

            {% if reservation.solidarityAmount > 0 %}
                <div class="impact-box">
                    <span class="impact-pill">Billet solidaire</span>
                    <p><strong>Association soutenue :</strong> {{ reservation.solidarityAssociation }}</p>
                    <p><strong>Contribution :</strong> {{ reservation.solidarityAmount|number_format(2, ',', ' ') }} TND</p>
                    <p><strong>Code recu :</strong> {{ reservation.solidarityReceiptCode }}</p>
                    <p>Merci. Votre reservation contribue aussi a un impact local utile dans l ecosystème associatif de Tunis.</p>
                </div>
            {% endif %}

            <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;">
                <a href="{{ url('app_evenement_show', {'id': reservation.evenement.id}) }}" class="btn">Voir l evenement</a>
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>GrowMind - Bien-etre et developpement personnel</p>
            <p>Cet email sert aussi de billet d entree. Gardez-le sur votre telephone.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
